, 
<figureCitation box="[342,389,579,603]" captionStart="Figure 124-128" captionStartId="50.[192,276,1356,1378]" captionTargetBox="[198,1431,235,1320]" captionTargetId="figure-18@50.[193,1443,194,1361]" captionTargetPageId="50" captionText="Figure 124-128. Venation and some secondary sexual characters of male Porphyrogenes. Shown is ventral surface including modification of vein 2A and extent of speculum on ventral forewing (irregular line in CuA -2A and anal 2 cell) and origins of veins on hindwing. Insert is of anterior portion of dorsal hindwing showing hair-like tufts. 124) P. zohra, HONDURAS (GTA 8903); 125) P. convexus, holotype, BRAZIL:Rondônia (GTA 2760); 126) P. splendidus, holotype, BOLIVIA (GTA 4182); 127) P. simulator, holotype, BOLIVIA (GTA 4181); 128) P. spadix, holotype, BRAZIL: Rondônia (GTA 3894)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5169716" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5169716/files/figure.png" pageId="22" pageNumber="21">125</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation box="[400,445,579,603]" captionStart="Figure 140-145" captionStartId="53.[193,277,1693,1715]" captionTargetBox="[286,1354,216,1653]" captionTargetId="figure-137@53.[266,1371,194,1665]" captionTargetPageId="53" captionText="Figure 140-145. Male genitalia of Porphyrogenes; shown are lateral view of uncus, gnathos, tegumen, and saccus; dorsal view of uncus and tegumen; ventral view of uncus and gnathos; juxta; lateral view (with extended vesica) and often dorsal view of aedeagus; internal lateral view of right valva (inset shows the flattened harpe). 140) P. sororcula, BRAZIL: Rondônia (GTA 3493); 141) P. spanda (also including posterior view of harpe), BRAZIL: Rondônia (GTA 3225); 142) P. stresa (also including posterior view of harpe), BRAZIL: Rondônia (GTA 3927); 143) P. zohra (also including posterior view of harpe), HONDURAS (GTA 8903); 144) P. convexus, holotype, BRAZIL: Rondônia (GTA 2760); 145) P. splendidus (also including interior view of left valva), holotype, BOLIVIA (GTA 4182)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5169722" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5169722/files/figure.png" pageId="22" pageNumber="21">144</figureCitation>
